OL,3,CHow female gorillas find their next
OL,4,Cfriendship group
OL,6,FIn the animal kingdom, it is not rare
OL,7,Ffor individuals to leave their birth
OL,8,Fgroup and find another one.
OL,10,FThis process is known as dispersal and
OL,11,Fis key to reproduction.
OL,13,FDispersal prevents inbreeding, helps
OL,14,Fspread gene diversity and shapes
OL,15,Fsocial relationships.
OL,17,FThe research's findings have been
OL,18,Fshaped by more than 20 years of data
OL,19,Fon wild mountain gorillas.
