OL,3,CHow female gorillas find their next
OL,4,Cfriendship group
OL,6,FThe study, which was published in
OL,7,FProceedings of the Royal Society B,
OL,8,Frevealed that female gorillas do not
OL,9,Fdisperse randomly and that past social
OL,10,Fexperiences help them to make their
OL,11,Fdecision.
OL,13,FGroup size and gender ratio do not
OL,14,Fseem to have the same impact on
OL,15,Fdecision-making as those remembered
OL,16,Fencounters.
