OL,3,CHow female gorillas find their next
OL,4,Cfriendship group
OL,6,FThe most influential female
OL,7,Frelationships were with those female
OL,8,Fgorillas who they had spent at least
OL,9,Ffive years getting to know and had
OL,10,Fseen within the last two.
OL,12,F"Going into a new group could feel
OL,13,Fpretty scary, with individuals usually
OL,14,Fentering at the bottom of the social
OL,15,Fhierarchy. A familiar female might
OL,16,Fhelp reduce this, providing a social
OL,17,Fally," says Dr Robin Morrison, senior
OL,18,Fauthor of the study.
