OL,3,CHow female gorillas find their next
OL,4,Cfriendship group
OL,6,F"It could also act like a
OL,7,Frecommendation from a friend - if a
OL,8,Ffemale they know has chosen to stay in
OL,9,Fthis group, it could indicate positive
OL,10,Fthings about the group as a whole or
OL,11,Fthe dominant male leading that group."
OL,13,FBut what about male acquaintances?
OL,15,FIn contrast to their female
OL,16,Ffriendships, the female gorilla will
OL,17,Favoid males they grew up with.
