OL,3,CHow female gorillas find their next
OL,4,Cfriendship group
OL,6,F"Because female mountain gorillas do
OL,7,Fnot know with certainty who their
OL,8,Ffathers are, they might rely on a
OL,9,Fsimple rule like 'avoid any group with
OL,10,Fmales I grew up with', lead
OL,11,Fresearcher, Victoire Martignac said.
OL,13,FThis is because "the likelihood of
OL,14,Fthem being related will be higher than
OL,15,Fwith males they did not grow up with.
